        itineraire: "From Nice, take the A8 motorway towards Cannes / Aix-en-Provence. After 28 km, take exit 42 'Mougins'. Follow the D35 uphill for 2 km to reach the perched old village. The village is pedestrianised: the driver drops you at the Porte Sarrazine car park, at the entrance to the medieval town. The journey crosses the wooded hills above Sophia Antipolis, with views over the Brague valley. For a more scenic route, you can take the D6085 via the Grasse road, but it adds 15 minutes.",
